    <title>hexo文章快速生成指令查阅</title>
    <url>/2025/10/14/hexo%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8Ahexo%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E6%9F%A5%E9%98%85/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="先配置环境"><a href="#先配置环境" class="headerlink" title="先配置环境"></a>先配置环境</h4><ul>
<li>github端：</li>
</ul>
<ol>
<li>新建一个私有仓库放源码，防止你的内容被篡改，名  hexo-source（随意取） ，不要readme </li>
<li>新建一个公有的仓库（GitHub Pages要求公开才能访问），名为 用户名.github.io  ，这里用户名，是要和github上的用户名对应的，就是登录github的用户名。这个仓库作用是用自动化脚本从源码位置搞成网页放过去，不要readme</li>
<li>生成令牌<br>Github头像→Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → Tokens(classic) → 勾选 repo全部权限 → 复制令牌 </li>
<li>把Token密钥存进私有仓库<br>私有仓库 → Settings → Secrets and variables → New repository secret → Name 填  PAGES_TOKEN  → Value 贴刚才的令牌</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>本地：</li>
</ul>
<ol>
<li>装Node.js<br><a href="https://nodejs.org/">https://nodejs.org/</a></li>
<li>装git</li>
<li>装hexo</li>
</ol>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">hexo version   # 看到版本号说明 OK</span><br><span class="line">hexo init my-blog</span><br><span class="line">cd my-blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install # 装依赖</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save #安装自动部署插件</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#本地跑一下看看能不能出东西</span><br><span class="line">hexo server            # 或 hexo s</span><br><span class="line"># 浏览器打开 http://localhost:4000 能看到默认页面即可</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl+C 停掉</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>

<ul>
<li>自动化部署脚本（GitHub Actions 自动部署）<br>每次你推送源码到私有仓库 ，GitHub Actions 会自动构建静态文件，并推送到公开仓库。别人只能看到构建后的静态文件，看不到源码和文章原始内容。<br>具体使用:<br>先生成github action 脚本</li>
</ul>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir -p .github/workflows</span><br><span class="line">touch .github/workflows/deploy.yml</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>
<p> 在本地文件的  .github&#x2F;workflows&#x2F;deploy.yml放入下面的代码,注意用户名用自己的。</p>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">name: 自动部署 Hexo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">on:</span><br><span class="line">  push:</span><br><span class="line">    branches: [ main ]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">jobs:</span><br><span class="line">  build:</span><br><span class="line">    runs-on: ubuntu-latest</span><br><span class="line">    steps:</span><br><span class="line">      - uses: actions/checkout@v4</span><br><span class="line">      - uses: actions/setup-node@v4</span><br><span class="line">        with:</span><br><span class="line">          node-version: 18</span><br><span class="line">          cache: &#x27;npm&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">      - run: npm ci</span><br><span class="line">	  - run: npx hexo clean #清理一下旧缓存</span><br><span class="line">      - run: npx hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">      - uses: peaceiris/actions-gh-pages@v4</span><br><span class="line">        with:</span><br><span class="line">          personal_token: $&#123;&#123; secrets.PAGES_TOKEN &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">          external_repository: maomaogongzi/maomaogongzi.github.io</span><br><span class="line">          publish_branch: main</span><br><span class="line">          publish_dir: ./public</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>


<p>先进入第一次提交</p>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;first hexo&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git branch -M main</span><br><span class="line">git remote add origin https://github.com/github的用户名/hexo-source.git</span><br><span class="line">git push -u origin main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>

<h4 id="对于跨机子操作"><a href="#对于跨机子操作" class="headerlink" title="对于跨机子操作"></a>对于跨机子操作</h4><ol>
<li>需要先配置环境</li>
<li>git clone 源码库</li>
<li><code>npm isntall</code> 装一下依赖</li>
<li>然后就是<code>hexo new &quot;文章名&quot;</code></li>
<li>然后git三部曲，添加，消息，推送</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="如果是用Windows-PowerShell"><a href="#如果是用Windows-PowerShell" class="headerlink" title="如果是用Windows PowerShell"></a>如果是用Windows PowerShell</h4><p>会出现禁止运行脚本的报错<br>用下面代码临时允许脚本<br><code>Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass </code><br>然后继续操作即可<br>也可以永久运行<br><code>Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope CurrentUser -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned </code></p>
<h4 id="告诉git你是谁"><a href="#告诉git你是谁" class="headerlink" title="告诉git你是谁"></a>告诉git你是谁</h4><p>涉及到提交git的用户名和注册邮箱，提交git会有记录，这个就是记录</p>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;你的GitHub用户名&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;你的GitHub注册邮箱&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>

<h4 id="初始化git的问题"><a href="#初始化git的问题" class="headerlink" title="初始化git的问题"></a>初始化git的问题</h4><p>初始化git的时候，应该是在里面那层文件夹里初始化，源文件所在的地方，不要到外面那一层自己新建文件夹初始化，理论上也可以，但是脚本里的位置是以里层做的，所以如果git到外一层，可能会因为路径不对，脚本报错。注意这个问题</p>
<h4 id="LF报错"><a href="#LF报错" class="headerlink" title="LF报错"></a>LF报错</h4><p>遇到LF问题的报错，这是 Windows 与 Unix 换行符差异 的提示，完全无害，可以忽略。</p>
<h4 id="git网络报错"><a href="#git网络报错" class="headerlink" title="git网络报错"></a>git网络报错</h4><p>遇到网络问题，git不能push或clone等操作，挂代理，先打开自己代理，然后输入命令</p>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http.proxy http://127.0.0.1:7890</span><br><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy http://127.0.0.1:7890</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>

<p>注意这个7890端口是clash的，其他代理软件需要自己再查查<br>配置后，重新使用git </p>
<p>放心，只有git命令会走代理<br>如果不再需要用git走代理，用下面这个命令</p>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --unset http.proxy</span><br><span class="line">git config --global --unset https.proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>
<h4 id="版本问题"><a href="#版本问题" class="headerlink" title="版本问题"></a>版本问题</h4><p>可能会遇到一些版本问题，用7.3.0版本的hexo稳定，新的hexo插件暂时还没支持，在package.json里改。</p>
<h4 id="hexo文章生成，常用命令"><a href="#hexo文章生成，常用命令" class="headerlink" title="hexo文章生成，常用命令"></a>hexo文章生成，常用命令</h4><div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd my-blog                        # 进入项目根目录</span><br><span class="line">hexo new &quot;我的文章标题&quot;           # 自动生成md文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>

<p>用Obsidian去打开，如果没有Typora，需要用Obsidian，但是这个软件不能直接双击打开md，要先去软件里，设置仓库，左下角。设置你放md文件的仓库，然后就会显示。</p>
<p>同时，如果有多个仓库，新仓库的主题不会继承旧仓库。但是可以直接去旧仓库主题的文件夹，复制到新仓库这里。就也能用。</p>
<p>写文件的时候，如果要发布在hexo上，需要注意写的格式，Obsidian默认头部会包含格式。如果用Typora，需要注意tags那一栏的东西需要也能改中括号包裹。</p>
<p>写完用<br><code>hexo server</code><br>命令，本地实时预览效果</p>
<p>每次生成新文件后</p>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean      # 可选：清缓存</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate   # 生成静态文件（CI 会自动做，本地也可手动）</span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;post: 我的文章标题&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git push        # Actions  跑完即上线 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>

<h4 id="主题设置"><a href="#主题设置" class="headerlink" title="主题设置"></a>主题设置</h4><ul>
<li><a href="https://hexo.io/themes/index.html">Themes | Hexo</a><br>一般从官方主题那就有很多，也可以找找很多没有收录进来的主题。</li>
<li>可以看看github上的主题说明，以下是比较通用的部分。</li>
</ul>
<p>以Meow主题为例</p>
<ol>
<li>首先安装git该主题的库，指定下载位置，不然下载下来是hexo-theme-meow，和配置文件会对应不上<br><code>git clone -b main https://github.com/chanwj/hexo-theme-meow.git themes/meow</code></li>
<li>修改根目录下的的配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，将主题更换为meow</li>
<li>然后进行渲染<code>npm install hexo-renderer-pug --save</code></li>
<li>如果没有Stylus渲染器（在package.json中检查）<br><code>npm install hexo-renderer-stylus --save</code></li>
<li>以上只是安装步骤，但是安装完还需要配置，现在还不能用</li>
<li>由于clone主题仓库的时候带了一个.git的隐藏文件夹，刚练手建议先删了，不然会有警告。如果需要更新这个仓库，再说。</li>
<li>第一次使用会报错，要先去主题配置文件下找到sidebar的links的list，在该条目下面不能为空，要写一些东西，写一些个人的仓库地址，知乎地址等内容。总之，不允许为空</li>
</ol>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sidebar:</span><br><span class="line">  # 其他侧边栏配置...</span><br><span class="line">  links:</span><br><span class="line">    enable: true  # 确保侧边栏链接模块「启用」</span><br><span class="line">    title: 我的链接  # 侧边栏链接区域的标题（可自定义）</span><br><span class="line">    list:  # 必须添加「链接名称: 链接地址」的键值对，示例如下：</span><br><span class="line">      GitHub: https://github.com/你的用户名</span><br><span class="line">      个人博客: https://你的博客域名</span><br><span class="line">      知乎: https://www.zhihu.com/people/你的知乎ID</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>
<ol start="8">
<li>另一个报错是搜索插件问题，先<code>npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</code>然后需要去根目录的配置文件下面，添加下面几行,注意，yml文件有严格格式要求，缩进要注意，不然依然会报错。（第7点同样也是要注意格式）</li>
</ol>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 搜索功能配置（用于Meow主题）</span><br><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml  # 搜索索引文件路径，必须有这个参数</span><br><span class="line">  field: post       # 搜索范围：post（仅文章）、page（仅页面）、all（全部）</span><br><span class="line">  content: true     # 是否搜索文章内容</span><br><span class="line">  format: html      # 内容格式</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>
<p>回到主题的配置文件，要把search段enable改成true</p>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true  # 启用搜索功能</span><br><span class="line">  type: local   # 搜索类型（当前仅支持local）</span><br><span class="line">  local:</span><br><span class="line">    top_n_per_article: 1  # 每篇文章显示的搜索结果条数</span><br><span class="line">    preload: false        # 是否预加载搜索数据</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>
<ol start="9">
<li>然后就是清理缓存，重新生成静态文件，启动服务，最后本地访问看看。</li>
<li>最后推送到github上时候，会遇到一些问题，如果遇到你的主题文件夹在github上打不开，是灰色，或者出现了个箭头，但是看不到子文件夹，是因为这个主题是从别人的仓库里clone下来的，会带上.git的隐藏文件夹，会被github认为是嵌套仓库的机制。主仓库只会记录子模块的仓库地址和版本指针，而非子模块的文件内容。所以在本地文件的主题文件夹里的.git文件删掉。但是此时你的本地仓库不认为这是一次改动，所以推不上去，他无法识别到变化。这是因为有git的子模块混存，所以对缓存进行删除。<code>git rm --cached themes/meow</code></li>
<li>然后重新提交</li>
</ol>
<div class="code-container" code-lang="Plaintext"><div class="codebox"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git add themes/meow # 将主题文件夹作为普通文件添加到暂存区 </span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;移除子模块缓存，提交主题文件夹（含CSS、JS等静态资源）&quot; # 提交修改 </span><br><span class="line">git push # 推送到GitHub远程仓库</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="code-fold" title="Fold/Open"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M6 9l6 6l6 -6" /></svg></div><div class="code-copy" title="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M7 7m0 2.667a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 -2.667h8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 2.667h-8.666a2.667 2.667 0 0 1 -2.667 -2.667z" /><path d="M4.012 16.737a2.005 2.005 0 0 1 -1.012 -1.737v-10c0 -1.1 .9 -2 2 -2h10c.75 0 1.158 .385 1.5 1" /></svg></div></div></div>


]]></content>
